<template name="zeroBuyRemind">
  <view class='share-sm' catchtouchmove='preventTouchMove'>
    <view class='sign-finish-top'>
      <text class='sign-finish-top-title'>0元购说明</text>
      <image catchtap="bindTapcCloseShareTX" class='icon-close' src="{{Upyun}}small-iconImages/gx/iconwhiteclose.png"></image>
    </view>
    <scroll-view class='srcoll-vv' scroll-y='true'>
      <view class='view-item-yugao-sm'>
        <text class='yugao-count-sm'>1</text>
        <text class='mingri-text' style='font-size: 25rpx'>购买美衣并交易成功后直接返还全部金额至账户余额，能用来抵扣下次购衣款，及抽取1-1000元不等的提现现金。</text>
      </view>
      <view class='view-item-yugao-sm'>
        <text class='yugao-count-sm'>2</text>
        <text class='mingri-text' style='font-size: 25rpx'>每消费1元获得一个衣豆。可用来抽取1-1000元不等的提现现金。每次消耗10衣豆。</text>
      </view>
    </scroll-view>
  </view>
